<i>Because it's the only way</i>

18
00:01:23.817 --> 00:01:30.089  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>Follow it</i>
<i>The small hope I aim for</i>

19
00:01:30.156 --> 00:01:33.159  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:79.33% 
<i>The weakness that spilled</i>
<i>From the proffered hand</i>

20
00:01:33.226 --> 00:01:36.362  position:50.00%,middle  align:middle size:80.00%  line:84.67% 
